<h1 >Guide to Social Security Law Updates - 1996</h1>
<ul><li><a href="1996#12december1996">12 December 1996</a></li>
<li><a href="1996#1december1996">1 December 1996</a></li>
<li><a href="1996#28november1996">28 November 1996</a></li>
<li><a href="1996#31october1996">31 October 1996</a></li>
<li><a href="1996#17october1996">17 October 1996</a></li>
<li><a href="1996#3october1996">3 October 1996</a></li>
<li><a href="1996#19september1996">19 September 1996</a></li>
<li><a href="1996#5september1996">5 September 1996</a></li>
<li><a href="1996#22august1996">22 August 1996</a></li>
<li><a href="1996#8august1996">8 August 1996</a></li>
<li><a href="1996#25july1996">25 July 1996</a></li>
<li><a href="1996#11july1996">11 July 1996</a></li>
