<h2>Update 616G # Date 4 April 1996</h2>
<p>CHAPTER 23 - ADDITIONAL PAYMENTS - RENT ASSISTANCE, PHARMACEUTICAL ALLOWANCE, TELEPHONE ALLOWANCE, REMOTE AREA ALLOWANCE - Advance pharmaceutical allowance. See guidelines 23.3270 to 23.3322.</p>
<p>After pension records are converted to the new systems architecture known as Common Platform, payment of Advance pharmaceutical allowance can be made to each (or either) member of a couple as an individual. To date this has not been possible due to limitations with the previous pensions system.</p>
